Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.44,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.60,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.16,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.30,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:22.65,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:27.38,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:34.32,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama! Where are we going, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know... Where shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunset was so beautiful... it made me forget where we were going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would you like to go, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Anywhere! I'll go anywhere you want, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei, it will be up to you to protect your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Your real sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You, at least, can be with me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...but your sister cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How come? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She was adopted...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She was taken away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,33. Take Flight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, in our campaign to abolish the Sorority,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...we have signatures of two-thirds of the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We have presented the petition to the school board.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it is Saturday morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san! Tomoko-san! It's out, finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The response! From the school board!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's posted on the bulletin board!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... what does it say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"With regard to the matter of the abolition of the Sorority,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:04:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...the school board has scheduled an emergency session in one week."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...signed, "Seiran School Board."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...the petition has finally forced the school officials to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sorority... it's been involved in so much that has happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't deny having mixed feelings regarding the Sorority,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...but at least this will put the matter to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you seem happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all over now? I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All over?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I of no use to her anymore? I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that even if the Sorority is abolished completely,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...she would carry on exactly as she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Her dignified persona...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...amidst her unraveling beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pride cannot be attained unless it is longed for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore I will continue to long for it always...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...regardless of what may happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I trembled with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here was the proud Fukiko-sama I knew when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She was herself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In all the issues concerning the Sorority and the petition,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...the beauty of Fukiko-sama outshone everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the happiness I have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This strange happiness feels new to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how long it can last.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I had such a good night's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Good for you, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too slow, Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense! You just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,First place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn, second place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There might be no one home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we'd called first...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok then. now let's race to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. This time I'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi-san has been driving us around in his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We were visiting real estate agencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Real estate agencies?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mother and I are looking for a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for a large one, just a house for Mother and I to live happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My Brother... it was the first I'd heard of her moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The divorce is final now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come inside. I'm serving Assam tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Assam tea? That'll be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, were you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... uh... was there any for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No. But I'll make some especially for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, male guests aren't invited into the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I do hope this is to your liking, Ichinomiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, creme brule?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually quite fond of sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, of course! This is quite an occasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No more of your nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok! Yes Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san and her mother are trying to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If there were anything at all I could do, I wanted to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Help for Mariko-san in her new life...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya-san was probably trying to help her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Father? Fukiko-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a telephone call for you. From London.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness! From Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Yes, everyone is very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, you were telling me about that last time you called.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my brother has returned now also.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I put him on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he'd rather not also.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh father, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to be concerned about the Sorority events.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more like you than I'm willing to admit, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei? You asked about Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's her usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, she seems to be happier these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself too, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unusual... Father asking about Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always concerned about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When we talk on the telephone, he always asks about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for asking you to meet me so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank me? For what I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe... but no, not about that, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To someone like you... pure... warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...sensitive, but strong as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So very pretty too... I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting strange... Very strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Do I sound strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... saying those things... about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But suddenly it feels right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being completely sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the skyline is lovely, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then everything's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The lights are very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She... Fukiko-sama... she is not my step sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my true sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She joined the family by adoption right after she was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She is my full sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just before Mother passed away, she told me the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...and asked me to take care of her, to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...and to never tell Fukiko-sama the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother wanted Fukiko-sama to be happy, and part of the Ichinomiya family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother left the world as just a lonely lover, unable to marry,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...and with that one final wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Living with my mother gave me such happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is up to me to protect Fukiko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:13:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect her pride. My life depends on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why confide in me? These are such important facts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To give them to me... to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that reason enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... my heart has found great strength for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes... I'd like to show you the sunset tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I know of a place where you can see the most beautiful sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother often took me there when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret. Shall we go there tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Yes! I would love to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather far to go, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother... the day was very hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There were no clouds in the sky, the sun was shining brightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,By six in the morning I was already awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was to meet Saint-Juste-sama at three that afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I couldn't simply sit around waiting,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I left the house at about a quarter after eleven.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now see here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Don't be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I make plans to do things on Sundays, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't invite me out on last minute outings!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll buy you cake. And tea too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's blazing hot out today! And I'm in a really lousy mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go to a teahouse with air conditioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You have makeup on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A tiny bit. As a sunblock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? You're up to something today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Till 2:30... no, 2:15 is fine. Just stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Ah, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Just... cleaning up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unusual. I guess Hell froze over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I got up this morning, I felt really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Then you can come to practice right? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You should raise a sweat on a hot day like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? You can't? You have plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn, too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Like raindrops falling into cracks in the ground..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I found the book you loaned me. It was under the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Verlaine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"Teardrops are falling on my heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't go with today's weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't go with you, today, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get it back to you on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So... who are you meeting and where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so secretive, sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Something from the 17th century, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Rei will be there as expected?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to tell her that Father was asking about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think she is still taking pills?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are okay now. I think she stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She is actually a very sincere and happy girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I heard you say something good about Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll go wash my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? With Saint-Juste-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez. You should have said so from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunset. I'm going to go see the sunset with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"You need to lock your door when you're not home!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec... It's a little crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful! Your face gives away everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wham!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you make a delivery before the day is out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if it's at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If it's in the city, we can deliver it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, could I have the bouquet of roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and this one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, is that to be delivered as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No. This is for someone I am going to see today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Our rendezvous was a tiny station, far outside the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I arrived 15 minutes early, well before evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I could see the ocean from there. It was still sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I just watched the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.88,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right, I'm all right. Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny... my shoelace...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunset is so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss? Miss Fukiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a telephone call for you. From the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:22:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.17,0:23:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Ichinomiya residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko! What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.30,0:23:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei... Rei is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother... I waited and waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.07,0:23:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited, knowing that Saint-Juste-sama would be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.91,0:24:14.11,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.11,0:24:19.58,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.05,0:24:25.19,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:30.66,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.40,0:24:36.94,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.94,0:24:42.41,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.41,0:24:45.14,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.14,0:24:47.95,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.95,0:24:50.35,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.35,0:24:55.62,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
